content.text: The France-Singapore Digital and Green Partnership (DGP) is part of Singapore’s larger strategy to build a network of international partnerships that enable our companies, especially SMEs, to seize growth opportunities in the fast-growing digital and green economies. The DGP provides a structured platform for France and Singapore to cooperate on a wide range of digital and green issues.
